"},{"character":"Samwise Gamgee","relationship":"Guided by him"},{"character":"Merry Brandybuck","relationship":"Guided by him"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Guided by him"}],"recentEvents":"Guided and protected the hobbits from the Black Riders, leading them back to the Road and to the village of Bree."},{"name":"Goldberry","aliases":["Queen of the River"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Strider","currentLocation":"House near the village of Stock","description":"The wife of Tom Bombadil, she is known as the Queen of the River and is believed to have some magical or mystical powers associated with water.","relationships":[{"character":"Tom Bombadil","relationship":"Spouse"},{"character":"Merry","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Pippen","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Frodo","relationship":"Guest"}],"recentEvents":"Welcomed the hobbits, served them a supper and sang songs."},{"name":"Barliman Butterbur","aliases":["Mr. Butler","Barley"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Strider","currentLocation":"The Prancing Pony","description":"Landlord of The Prancing Pony and supplier of rumors.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Landlord"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Regular patron"}],"recentEvents":"Dealt with the confusion caused by Frodo's sudden disappearance."},{"name":"Aragorn","aliases":["Thorongil","Dúnadan","Strider","Elessar"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Farewell to Lórien","currentLocation":"Imladris (Rivendell)","description":"A Dúnadan and heir to the kingdom of Gondor, later known as Elessar Telcontar after becoming King.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Guided him to Rivendell"},{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Fellow traveler"}],"recentEvents":"Joined the merrymaking in the Hall of Fire and sat beside the Lady Arwen while Elrond and Arwen conversed."},{"name":"Mugwort","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","last_seen":"Strider","currentLocation":"The Prancing Pony","description":"A local Hobbit who witnessed Frodo's vanishing act.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Asserted he saw Frodo vanish into thin air, causing an uproar."},{"name":"Nob","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Unknown","currentLocation":"The Prancing Pony","description":"An inn servant who helps Frodo and his companions.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"servant and confidant"},{"character":"Merry Brandybuck","relationship":"servant and confidant"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"servant and confidant"}],"recentEvents":"Nob assists in the preparation and safety arrangements of the hobbits' rooms at the Prancing Pony Inn."},{"name":"Glorfindel","aliases":["Elrond's emissary"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"At the Ford of Bruinen","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"An Elf-lord who aids the Fellowship against Sauron's forces.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Savior and guide"}],"recentEvents":"Glorfindel led the white horse to speed past the riders, then called forth a flood upon the Riders who pursued Frodo."},{"name":"Lindir","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Council of Elrond","currentLocation":"Imladris (Rivendell)","description":"An Elf of Rivendell who spoke with Bilbo about his poem.","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Servant"}],"recentEvents":"Expressed appreciation for Bilbo's poem and conversed with him about its elements."},{"name":"Arwen","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Farewell to Lórien","currentLocation":"Imladris (Rivendell)","description":"Daughter of Elrond, pledged to Aragorn.","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Father"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Betrothed"}],"recentEvents":"Joined the merrymaking in the Hall of Fir