e","characters":["Sam"],"summary":"Sam, now aware of an early Council meeting, is taking responsibility for reminding Gandalf of Frodo's need for rest before the meeting."}],"summary":"Frodo rests in Rivendell, recovering from his journey with Bilbo's visits and conversations about music, poetry, and the beauty of nature. He witnesses Elvish celebrations and contemplates the perils and mysteries that surround them."},"model":"qwen2.5:14b","appVersion":"dev"},{"index":21,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"Bilbo Baggins","aliases":["Burglar","Master Ring-bearer","Uncle Bilbo","Bilbo","Belladonna Took's son","Baggy Bolger-Baggins","Thorin Oakenshield's Companion"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Shadow of the Past","currentLocation":"Rivendell","description":"A hobbit and explorer who found the One Ring; Frodo's uncle; the original Ring-bearer.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Uncle"},{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Self"}],"recentEvents":"Offered to accompany the Ring to destruction but was dissuaded by Gandalf."},{"name":"Gandalf the Grey","aliases":["the grey wizard","Mithrandir","Stormcloak","Gandalf"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Shadow of the Past","currentLocation":"Rivendell","description":"A wizard and leader of the Council of the Wise; Frodo's mentor and guide.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Teacher and Guide"},{"character":"Saruman the White","relationship":"Friend and Rival"}],"recentEvents":"Encouraged Frodo to take on the task of destroying the Ring and supported Sam in doing so."},{"name":"Frodo Baggins","aliases":["Mr. Underhill","Samwise's master","Elf-friend","Mr. Baggins","Frodo","The Ring-bearer","Underhill","Frodo, The Ring-bearer","Ring-bearer"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Shadow of the Past","currentLocation":"Rivendell","description":"A hobbit who inherited the One Ring from Bilbo Baggins; chosen to destroy the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Uncle"},{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Teacher and Guide"},{"character":"Samwise Gamgee","relationship":"Gardener and Best Friend"}],"recentEvents":"Volunteered to take the One Ring to destroy it, agreed to allow Sam to accompany him."},{"name":"Peregrin Took","aliases":["Pippin","Mr. Pippin Took","Peregrin","Mr. Took","Pippin Took"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"A Knife in the Dark","currentLocation":"Weathertop","description":"A young hobbit and friend of Merry's, who joins the journey from the Shire.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Friend and companion"},{"character":"Merry Brandybuck","relationship":" Cousin and friend"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Protector of Frodo"}],"recentEvents":"Pippin grew terrified and fell flat to the ground when the Black Riders charged."},{"name":"Meriadoc Brandybuck","aliases":["Merry","Master","Master Merry","Meriadoc","Mr. Brandybuck","Merry Brandybuck"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"A Knife in the Dark","currentLocation":"Weathertop","description":"A young hobbit and friend of Frodo's, who joins the journey from the Shire.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Friend and companion"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":" Cousin and friend"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Protector of Frodo"}],"recentEvents":"Merry saw the black figures approaching and shrank with fear during the attack."},{"name":"Elrond","importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Farewell to Lórien","currentLocation":"Imladris (Rivendell)","description":"The lord and master of Rivendell, an Elf-friend and wise leader.","relationships":[{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Host"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Host"}],"recentEvents":"Present at the merrymaking in the Hall of Fire.","aliases":["Elrond Half-elven"]}