 Merry","Meriadoc","Mr. Brandybuck","Merry Brandybuck"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"A Knife in the Dark","currentLocation":"Weathertop","description":"A young hobbit and friend of Frodo's, who joins the journey from the Shire.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Friend and companion"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":" Cousin and friend"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Protector of Frodo"}],"recentEvents":"Merry saw the black figures approaching and shrank with fear during the attack."},{"name":"Elrond","importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Farewell to Lórien","currentLocation":"Imladris (Rivendell)","description":"The lord and master of Rivendell, an Elf-friend and wise leader.","relationships":[{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Host"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Host"}],"recentEvents":"Present at the merrymaking in the Hall of Fire.","aliases":["Elrond Half-elven"]},{"name":"Galadriel","importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Many Years Ago","currentLocation":"Lórien","description":"Elven Queen who gave gifts to the Fellowship of the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Celeborn","relationship":"Husband"}],"recentEvents":"Departed from Middle-earth to the Undying Lands."},{"name":"Celeborn","importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Many Years Ago","currentLocation":"Lórien","description":"Elven Lord of Lórien and husband of Galadriel.","relationships":[{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Wife"}],"recentEvents":"Noted only as living in Lórien with Galadriel."},{"name":"Barahir","importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Many Years Ago","currentLocation":"Gondor","description":"Grandson of the Steward Faramir, author of the abbreviated version of The Tale of Aragorn and Arwen.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Wrote The Tale of Aragorn and Arwen for the history of Gondor."},{"name":"Findegil","importance":"minor","