},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"servant and confidant"}],"recentEvents":"Nob assists in the preparation and safety arrangements of the hobbits' rooms at the Prancing Pony Inn."},{"name":"Glorfindel","aliases":["Elrond's emissary","The Bright Elf"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Shadow of the Past","currentLocation":"Rivendell","description":"Elven lord and guardian; once lived in Imladris (Rivendell) and fought the greatest of the Nazgûl.","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond Halfelven","relationship":"Friend"},{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Host and Foe to Nazgûl"}],"recentEvents":"Supported the council's decision to take the Ring to Mount Doom."},{"name":"Lindir","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Council of Elrond","currentLocation":"Imladris (Rivendell)","description":"An Elf of Rivendell who spoke with Bilbo about his poem.","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Servant"}],"recentEvents":"Expressed appreciation for Bilbo's poem and conversed with him about its elements."},{"name":"Arwen","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Farewell to Lórien","currentLocation":"Imladris (Rivendell)","description":"Daughter of Elrond, pledged to Aragorn.","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Father"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Betrothed"}],"recentEvents":"Joined the merrymaking in the Hall of Fire and conversed with Elrond and Aragorn."},{"name":"Elrond Halfelven","aliases":["Lord Elrond","Lord of Rivendell"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Shadow of the Past","currentLocation":"Rivendell","description":"Elven lord of Rivendell, keeper of the Three Elven Rings, and host to the fellowship.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Friend"},{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Host and Patron for Long Time"}],"recentEvents":"Hosted a council to discuss the fate of th