ionship":"Formerly close, Aragorn guided Frodo but Frodo left alone to journey to Mordor"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Comrade in the Fellowship but now separated"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Comrade in the Fellowship but now separated"},{"character":"Sam","relationship":"Has a gardener and loyal companion who follows him"}],"recentEvents":"Departed alone in a boat after the fall of Boromir to follow his mission to destroy the One Ring, joined by Sam."},{"name":"Peregrin Took","aliases":["Pippin","Mr. Pippin Took","Peregrin","Mr. Took","Pippin Took","Pippin III","Pippin son of Paladin Took"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Voice of Saruman","currentLocation":"Nan Curunír","description":"A young hobbit and soldier of Gondor, known for his bravery and loyalty.","relationships":[{"character":"Merry","relationship":"Best friend"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Friend and leader"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Teacher and guide"}],"recentEvents":"Rode with Treebeard as the Ents marched to Isengard, witnessing the awakening of the Ents."},{"name":"Meriadoc Brandybuck","aliases":["Merry","Master","Master Merry","Meriadoc","Mr. Brandybuck","Merry Brandybuck","Merry III","Meryas"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Voice of Saruman","currentLocation":"Nan Curunír","description":"A young hobbit and fellow soldier of Gondor, known for his wisdom and courage.","relationships":[{"character":"Pippin","relationship":"Best friend"},{"character":"Sam","relationship":"Friend and fellow hobbit"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Friend and leader"}],"recentEvents":"Joined Treebeard in leading the Ents to destroy Isengard, seeing the Ents in action for the first time."},{"name":"Elrond","importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Farewell to Lórien","currentLocation":"Imladris (Rivendell)","description":"The lord and master of Rivendell, an Elf-friend and wise leader.","relationships":[{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Host"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Host"}],"recentEvents":"Present at the merrymaking in the Hall of Fire.","aliases":["Elrond Half-elven"]},{"name":"Galadriel","importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Lothlórien","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Galadriel is the Lady of Lórien and a powerful ruler and advisor to the Fellowship","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"has given guidance and a keepsake to"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"has a long history with"},{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"sister-wife to"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"father to"}],"recentEvents":"Galadriel waves the Fellowship farewell as they depart Lórien.","aliases":["Lady of the Golden Wood","Lady of Lórien","Elbereth"]},{"name":"Celeborn","importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Many Years Ago","currentLocation":"Lórien","description":"Elven Lord of Lórien and husband of Galadriel.","relationships":[{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Wife"}],"recentEvents":"Noted only as living in Lórien with Galadriel."},{"name":"Barahir","importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Many Years Ago","currentLocation":"Gondor","description":"Grandson of the Steward Faramir, author of the abbreviated version of The Tale of Aragorn and Arwen.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Wrote The Tale of Aragorn and Arwen for the history of Gondor."},{"name":"Findegil","importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Many Years Ago","currentLocation":"Minas Tirith","description":"King's Writer who completed the Thain's Book.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Completed a copy of the Red Book in Minas Tirith."},{"name":"Lobelia Sackville-Baggins","importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 3","currentLocation":"Bywater","description":"Hobbit from Sackville-Baggins family, rival of the Baggins family, known for her jealousy and desire to inherit Bag End.","relationships":[{"character":"Otho Sackville-Baggins","relationship":"Husband"},{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Rival"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Antagonist"}],"recentEvents":"Visited Frodo and pestered him about Bilbo's will, accusing him of being a Brandybuck."},{"name":"Samwise Gamgee","aliases":["Sam","Samwise","Sam Gamgee","Sammy","Sam Gardner","Hamfast's son","Hamfast Gamgee's Son"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Fellowship of the Ring","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Frodo's devoted gardener and servant, known for his unwavering loyalty and resourcefulness.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Formerly close, Aragorn guided Sam but Sam left after Boromir's death"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Comrade in the Fellowship but now separated"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Comrade in the Fellowship but now separated"},{"character":"Frodo","relationship":"Serves as his loyal companion and protector"}],"recentEvents":"Joined Frodo after Aragorn's guidance but without communicating his departure to the remaining Fellowship, left behind to follow Frodo to Mordor."},{"name":"Gildor","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"None","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"An Elf who encountered Frodo and his companions, giving them guidance and warning of peril.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Met and gave advice to"}],"recentEvents":"Met Frodo and gave him warnings about enemies and advised him to take friends with him."},{"name":"Farmer Maggot","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Shadow of the Past","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A farmer in the Shire known for his dogs and mushrooms.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Former enemy turned friend"},{"character":"Peregrin Took","relationship":"Former enemy turned friend"},{"character":"Meriadoc 