ents":"Welcomed the hobbits, served them a supper and sang songs."},{"name":"Barliman Butterbur","aliases":["Mr. Butler","Barley"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Strider","currentLocation":"The Prancing Pony","description":"Landlord of The Prancing Pony and supplier of rumors.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Landlord"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Regular patron"}],"recentEvents":"Dealt with the confusion caused by Frodo's sudden disappearance."},{"name":"Aragorn","aliases":["Thorongil","Dúnadan","Strider","Elessar","Dunedain Ranger","Estel","Aragorn, son of Arathorn","Arnor"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Helm's Deep","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Aragorn, known as Strider, is a descendant of the royal line of Gondor and a key figure in fighting Sauron.","relationships":[{"character":"Eowyn","relationship":"Admires/fancies"},{"character":"Théoden","relationship":"King and ally"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Close companion and ally"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Boromir's companion in the Fellowship"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Allied Wizard"},{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Father"},{"character":"Arwen","relationship":"Sister/Wife"},{"character":"Celebrían","relationship":"Mother"}],"recentEvents":"Assisted Théoden in defending Helm's Gate and charged down the ramparts at dawn to defeat Isengard's forces."},{"name":"Mugwort","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","last_seen":"Strider","currentLocation":"The Prancing Pony","description":"A local Hobbit who witnessed Frodo's vanishing act.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Asserted he saw Frodo vanish into thin air, causing an uproar."},{"name":"Nob","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Unknown","currentLocation":"The Prancing Pony","description":"An inn servant who helps Frodo and his companions.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","re