"relationship":"Host and Patron for Long Time"}],"recentEvents":"Hosted a council to discuss the fate of the One Ring and named Frodo as the Ring-bearer."},{"name":"Boromir","aliases":["Faramir's Big Brother","captain","Captain of Gondor"],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Fellowship of the Ring","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A Captain of Gondor who was deceived by the Ring and later redeemed himself before he died.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Friend and comrade"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Comrade in the Fellowship"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Comrade in the Fellowship"},{"character":"Frodo","relationship":"Attempted to take the Ring from him"},{"character":"Sam","relationship":"Servant of Frodo"}],"recentEvents":"Fell defending the remaining members of the Fellowship against the Uruk-hai and was killed."},{"name":"Legolas","aliases":["Greenleaf","Prince of Mirkwood","Elven Archer","Wood-elf"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Helm's Deep","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"An elf of Mirkwood, renowned as a warrior and marksman.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Close companion and ally"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Wizard ally"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Boromir's companion in the Fellowship"}],"recentEvents":"Assisted Aragorn in defending Helm's Gate and witnessed Gandalf's arrival."},{"name":"Gimli","aliases":["Son of Glóin","Dwarf","Gimli son of Glóin"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Black Gate Opens","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A dwarf of the Lonely Mountain and a trusted companion of Gandalf's.","relationships":[{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Travel Companion"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Travel Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Participates in the last muster with the Rohirrim."},{"name":"Haldir","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Fangorn Forest","currentLocation":"Cerin Amroth","description":"A guard of Lothlórien who escorts Frodo and Aragorn.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Guide to Lothlórien"}],"recentEvents":"Guided Frodo and Sam to Cerin Amroth and showed them the beauty of the place."},{"name":"Old Bent Man","aliases":["Old man with a hat"],"importance":"minor","status":"uncertain","lastSeen":"In the chapter describing Aragorn, Legolas, and Gimli's encounter","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"An elderly man seen by Gimli near the fire at night. He disappeared shortly after appearing.","relationships":[{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Seen by"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Seen by"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Seen by"}],"recentEvents":"Appeared by the fire at night and frightened the travelers, then vanished."},{"name":"Éomer","aliases":["Third Marshal of the Mark","Rohan's Captain of the Mark, Lord of the Mark"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Last Debate","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A valiant warrior and the king's nephew who leads the éoreds of the Rohirrim.","relationships":[{"character":"Théoden","relationship":"Nephew and Soldier"},{"character":"Éowyn","relationship":"Sister and Lady of Rohan"}],"recentEvents":"Leaves Edoras to join the host of Théoden."},{"name":"Uglúk","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"The Uruk-Hai","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Leader of a raiding party sent by either Isengard or Mordor, not clearly identified in the text","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Killed by Éomer at the edge of Fangorn Forest"},{"name":"Treebeard","aliases":["The Ent","The Ward of the Forest","Bregalad","The Marching Ent"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"March of the Ents","currentLocation":"Nan Curunír","description":"A young and enthusiastic Ent who joins the march to Isengard.","relationships":[{"character":"Treebeard","relationship":"Travel companion and fellow Ent"},{"character":"Pippin","relationship":"Rider on Treebeard"},{"character":"Merry","relationship":"Rider on Treebeard"}],"recentEvents":"Swung into the line of marching Ents beside Treebeard, joining the effort against Isengard."},{"name":"Théoden","aliases":["King of Rohan"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Helm's Deep","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"The king of Rohan, leader and warrior, distinguished by his golden shield and white horse, Shadowfax.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Wizard ally"},{"character":"Arnor","relationship":"Heir to the throne, ally"},{"character":"Erkenbrand","relationship":"Lord of Westfold"}],"recentEvents":"Charged down Helm's Deep ramparts at dawn to defeat Isengard's forces."},{"name":"Éowyn","aliases":["Lady of Rohan","Dernhelm"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The King of the Riders","currentLocation":"Edoras","description":"Théoden's bold and determined niece who serves both as a soldier and a noblewoman.","relationships":[{"character":"Théoden","relationship":"Uncle and Ruler"},{"character":"Éomer","relationship":"Uncle and Captain"}],"recentEvents":"Anointed as the leader of the Eorlingas in Théoden's absence."},{"name":"Háma","aliases":["Captain of the Guard"],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The King of the Golden Hall","currentLocation":"Edoras","description":"The chief guard of Théoden's court.","relationships":[{"character":"Théoden","relationship":"Guard"},{"character":"Éowyn","relationship":"Guard"},{"character":"Éomer","relationship":"Guard"}],"recentEvents":"Names Éowyn as the ruler of Rohan during Théoden's absence."},{"name":"Erkenbrand","aliases":["Lord of Westfold"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Helm's Deep","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A lord of Rohan who joined the battle at Helm's Deep with his forces.","relationships":[{"character":"